---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-writing"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-pos-writing"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--wide wheat-px-6 wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-items-center wheat-gap-16">
        <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-writing-visual wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-p-8 wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center">
            <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-overflow-hidden wheat-opacity-30">
                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-pos-writing-matrix wheat-font-mono wheat-pointer-events-none select-none">
                    10101010101010101010101010101010 01010101010101010101010101010101
                    11001100110011001100110011001100 ...
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-writing-glyph-wrapper wheat-text-center">
                <div class="wheat-text-6xl wheat-text-8xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-pos-writing-glyph wheat-mb-4">
                    Aleph
                </div>
                <div class="wheat-text-xs wheat-pos-writing-glyph-sub wheat-uppercase">
                    El inicio de la historia
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-pos-writing-content wheat-space-y-8">
            <span class="wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block trigo-positive-chapter">
                La Escritura
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-pos-writing-title">La Memoria Eterna</h2>
            <p class="wheat-text-lg wheat-pos-writing-desc-primary wheat-leading-relaxed">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="No inventamos la escritura para escribir poesía. La inventamos para contar sacos de trigo."
                />
            </p>
            <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-pos-writing-desc-secondary wheat-leading-relaxed">
                Pero esa herramienta contable se convirtió en algo más grande. Nos permitió hablar
                con los muertos y dejar mensajes a los no nacidos. El trigo nos obligó a crear la <strong class="wheat-font-bold wheat-pos-writing-strong">Historia</strong>.
            </p>
            <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-pos-writing-desc-secondary wheat-leading-relaxed">
                Sin el excedente de grano, nuestra memoria se borraría con cada generación. Con el
                trigo, nuestra experiencia se acumula. Somos inmortales en papel.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-pos-writing {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-visual {
        height: 50vh;
        background-color: #0c0a09;
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-matrix {
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        font-size: 10px;
        color: #065f46;
        line-height: 1;
        white-space: pre;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-glyph-wrapper {
        z-index: 10;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-glyph {
        color: #10b981;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-glyph-sub {
        color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6);
        letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-desc-primary {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-desc-secondary {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-writing-strong {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-pos-writing-content {
            order: 2;
        }
        .wheat-pos-writing-visual {
            order: 1;
        }
        .wheat-space-y-8 > * + * {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
